file.name: publicity_put.yml
file.content:
Update publicity for owner of current token
---
openapi: 3.0.0
components:
  securitySchemes:
    bearerAuth:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: JWT
security:
  - bearerAuth: []
consumes:
  "application/json"
tags:
  - name: "User"
parameters:
  - in: header
    name: Authorization
    description: "Send like this: Bearer [TOKEN]"
    type: string
    required: true
  - name: body
    in: body
    required: true
    schema:
      properties:
        publicity:
          type: boolean
          required: true
        
responses:
  200:
    description: "Publicity updated."
    schema:
      type: object
      properties:
        msg:
          type: string
          description: "Publicity updated."
      example:
        msg: "Publicity updated."
  500:
    description: "Server Error!"
    schema:
      type: object
      properties:
        msg:
          type: string
          description: "Server Error!"
      example:
        msg: "Server Error!"

Error: unmarshal: json: cannot unmarshal string into Go value of type ogen.Alias
